{
  "id": "adv_main_01_18_02",
  "title": "星見編4章12話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_shed-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ただいま、麻奈\n……麻奈……？　いるよな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m home‚ Mana.\nMana? You’re there‚ aren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.1333333333333337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 6.06666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "……うん\nおかえり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah.\nWelcome back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 9.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "…………どうだ？\n少しは良くなったか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How are you?\nFeeling any better?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.066666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 13.0666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "どうだろう……\nはは。特に変わりはないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not sure.\nHaha. Nothing’s really changed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.266666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "プロの先生に見てもらったんでしょ。レッスン",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A professional coached their dance rehearsals today‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 18.066666666666702
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。イズミって先生だけど、琴乃達のレッスンの後\nさくら達の所にも来てくれたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. It was a woman named Izumi. After Moon Tempest’s rehearsal‚\nshe went to coach Sunny Peace‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 30.000000000000004
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "私も見てもらったことあるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She coached me before‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.000000000000004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くん、出張でいない時だったから\n会ってなかったと思うけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was when you were on a business trip.\nSo I don’t think you met her then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.99999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 38.599999999999994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、あの人に見てもらえたのか……ふふふ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… So she helped them rehearse. Hehehe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 45.431405925750695
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "あの人ね、見込みがないグループのレッスンは\n絶対に受けないって有名なんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’ll never coach anyone\nwho doesn’t have potential in her eyes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.33140592575072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "その人が、両方とも\n見てくれたってことか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that means\nshe saw potential in both groups?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.39807259241739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-mna008.m4a",
      "text": "うん。それだけ見込みがあるってこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Which means they really must have what it takes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.33140592575072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 57.36473925908409
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 61.70897970199584
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、それでさ。なんかもう、先生がいる間は\n俺の出番もないかなぁ、なんて思ったりして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About that… I get the feeling that with her there‚\nthere’s really no reason for me to be around the girls.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.64231303532915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 71.24231303532912
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-mna009.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You think so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.24231303532915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、だから明日は\nレッスンについていかなくても平気なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. So tomorrow‚\nI don’t have to go watch their rehearsals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.14231303532917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tears-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 77.80897970199582
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 77.80897970199582
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（いくら麻奈自身の望みとはいえ）\n（今の麻奈を放ってはおけなかった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(No matter what Mana’s actual wishes are‚)\n(I just can’t abandon her right now.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6089797019958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 83.1089797019958
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-mna010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ここにいちゃダメだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you can’t stay here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1089797019958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-mna011.m4a",
      "text": "グランプリのセミファイナルを前にしたグループを\n二つも抱えてるんだよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re managing Grand Prix semi-finalists.\nAnd two groups‚ at that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.83618244563827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-mna012.m4a",
      "text": "なのに、こんな所にいるようなマネージャーになって\nほしくないの。{user}くんには",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t want you to flake on your manager duties‚\nand hang out here with me‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.61158741315204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 99.74492074648533
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、さくらも芽衣も、自分達は大丈夫だからって\n麻奈の側にいてあげてほしいって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Sakura and Mei both said they’ll be fine.\nThey wanted me to go be with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.07825407981873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-mna013.m4a",
      "text": "そっか。要するに{user}くんは\n邪魔者扱いされてるってことかー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh. I presume‚ {user}‚\nthis means you’re annoying them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1115874131521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 115.44492074648508
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そうなの～～！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.44492074648544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（声を大きくして、俺は情けない声を出した）\n（もちろんわざとだ。麻奈の冗談に付き合ったのだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(My voice is loud and pathetic when I scream.)\n(I did that on purpose‚ of course. I was just playing along with Mana’s joke.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.31863951683049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 127.11863951683048
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-mna014.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……。つまらないなあ\n昔だったらすぐ本気にしたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe… Lame.\nIn the past‚ you would’ve taken my joke seriously.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.45197285016388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "少しは成長するよ。俺でも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve grown up‚ too. Believe it or not.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.21863951683056,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 138.51863951683055
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
